high_descs: turn to the right and go past the table and turn to the right and go to the counter and turn to the left facing the counter
pick up the head of lettuce from the counter top
turn to the right twice and go to the front of the sink and turn to the left facing the sink
put the head of lettuce in the sink and turn on the water to fill the sink and turn off and drain the water from the sink and pick up the head of lettuce from the sink
turn to the left and go to the counter and turn to the left and go past the stove and turn to the right and go to the waste basket
put the head of lettuce in the waste basket
anns.task_desc: Place a washed head of lettuce in the waste basket

high_descs: Turn around completely and walk forward then turn to the right. Face the other counter.
Pick up the lettuce from the counter.
Turn right and go to the sink. Turn left to face the sink.
Place the lettuce in the sink and wash it. Take out the lettuce.
Turn to the left and go around the corner. Turn right and go to the bin.
Place the lettuce inside the green bin.
anns.task_desc: Wash and move lettuce to a green bin.

high_descs: Turn around and cross to the opposite end of the kitchen, then face the counter to the left.
Pick up the lettuce that is near the wine bottle.
Face the opposite direction and take the lettuce to the sink ahead and to the left.
Wash the lettuce in the sink.
Turn to your left and go to the left side of the stove.
Put the lettuce in the green waste bin to the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Throw a clean head of lettuce away in a kitchen waste bin.
